The '''Producers Alliance for Cinema and Television''' ('''Pact''') is the UK [[trade association]] for independent content producers in feature film, television, animation, children's and [[digital media]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Who are we?|url=http://www.pact.co.uk/home/|work=Pact|accessdate=10 April 2012}}</ref>
Pact campaigns on issues of relevance to its members, including [[intellectual property]], diversity (Pact's members are invited to sign a voluntary Diversity Pledge<ref>{{cite web|title=Producers' Alliance for Cinema and Television|url=http://www.efd.org.uk/members/producers-alliance-for-cinema-and-television-pact|work=Employers Forum on Disability|accessdate=10 April 2012}}</ref>), and international issues.<ref>{{cite web|title=Campaigns|url=http://www.pact.co.uk/campaigns/|work=Pact|accessdate=10 April 2012}}</ref>
